Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:15.40,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:131319,135406}Unforgivable!\NThe Bad Guys Destroy a House.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141245,142872}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142872,144540}Good morning, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144540,147043}Hey, Meimi, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:29.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147919,149712}This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:33.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149712,153758}Isn't this a Miho-chan doll?\NI had one like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153758,159222}I found it cleaning my room. It brought\Nback memories so I brought it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:43.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159222,163351}I wonder if I still have mine.\NI'll try looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:49.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163351,169816}We girls have a lot of memories\Nin these dolls, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:53.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169816,173277}You girls are lucky to have\Nthat much time on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173277,175947}I don't even have time\Nto make memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:03:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175947,180535}I'm so busy trying\Nto catch St. Tail that…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:06.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181703,186916}Right. With all those memories of\NSt. Tail escaping, you're frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186916,188710}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:12.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188710,192338}If you don't like it,\Ntry catching her quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:17.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192338,197093}It'll be your most precious memory.\NThough it's probably impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:22.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197677,202515}Now you've said it! I'm not after\NSt. Tail for a reason like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202515,204809}Precious memories, what nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:31.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205935,211023}Is that so? Are you saying there are\Nno memories between you and St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212442,214485}Why are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214944,216404}How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216404,218072}My doll…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:44.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220825,224036}It disgusts me to know\Nwhat a dingbat that guy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:49.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224746,229000}Oh, my. We should be\Nthe ones appreciating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:53.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229792,233755}Why is that?\NHe's never done anything to save—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235465,238342}That's not true, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:02.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238342,242430}When you're angry, Meimi,\Nit's usually about Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242430,243681}Seira, you're mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:09.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244682,249312}Anyway, today there was another\Nlost sheep that wandered by here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250062,253483}A while ago, Michiru\Ncame by to ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:17.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253483,257737}She used to live happily\Nin a mansion with her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:23.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258279,263701}But one year ago, Michiru's father\Ncosigned a loan for a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263701,267622}and because of that,\Nthey lost their mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:35.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268498,275588}That friend he cosigned for\Ntook the loan money and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:40.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276380,280927}Not only did the loan company\Ntake control of the mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280927,283554}but everything inside of it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:50.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284639,290520}Michiru's jewelry box was a precious thing\Nfilled with all kinds of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291145,294816}Michiru hid the box in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:59.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294816,299904}Right after that, they were forced\Nto vacate the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:04.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300655,304617}Then that jewelry box is\Nstill hidden in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:09.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306160,309038}She was planning to get it back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:12.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309038,312083}But Negoro, who owns\Nthe loan company…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316128,318381}It's you again, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318381,321759}You'll get nowhere, no matter\Nhow many times you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321759,324178}Just for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324178,327849}I want to see the inside\Nof the house one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:32.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327849,332937}This house doesn't belong to you\Nanymore, young lady. It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:37.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334021,337400}Also, this land is being sold,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337400,341612}so we're gonna have\Nto tear down the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:47.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342196,347326}What will happen to her memories?\NThe jewelry box of memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:53.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348160,353291}There's nothing that can be done\Nabout Michiru's house being torn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:58.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353875,358254}Then at least the jewelry box\Nshould be returned to Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359046,361424}If it isn't, it'll be too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:05.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361424,365720}Ever since the house was taken,\NMichiru's mother has become ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367054,369974}They're breaking down\Nthe house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369974,372184}We only have tonight\Nto carry this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372602,375021}Let's get those memories back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382778,383863}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391287,392872}Is this a…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:39.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393539,399211}"Tonight, I'll be entering the Misaki mansion\Nto pick up a jewelry box. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399837,401964}It's a notice from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401964,405176}– A notice from St. Tail?\N– Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405176,408888}Don't push. I can't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416979,419231}So that's the Misaki mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423194,424403}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427031,429075}I'll leave tomorrow up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429075,430534}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:22.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436457,442713}This is really troublesome, isn't it?\NTearing down a mansion like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:27.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442713,447802}Making this an open lot is the terms\Nthe buyer made. What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447802,449804}It'll all be done by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450304,452932}We're finally getting to the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:38.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452932,458771}Didn't think that it'd go this smooth.\NLike a bubble on a wet hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:43.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458771,463025}Nobody would suspect that\Nyou borrowed the money and I lent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:51.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,471117}Not realizing a thing your cosigner Misaki\Nis either a real nice guy or an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:57.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471117,477081}– Oh, how my heart aches.\N– That guy picked a bad friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:00.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477081,480209}– Speak for yourself.\N– Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480209,482294}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482294,484130}Mr. Negoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484130,487758}I'm Asuka Jr. I'm assisting\Nin the St. Tail investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488217,490136}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:14.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490136,494223}Actually, we just received\Na notice from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:18.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494223,498477}She's going to appear here tonight\Nto steal a jewelry box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499061,501981}A jewelry box? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:25.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501981,505192}How could there be such a thing\Nin this unoccupied mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505985,508446}By the way, what's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508446,511073}Tomorrow we're clearing this lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511073,513617}You're going to tear it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:40.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516412,520875}If St. Tail is coming, there will\Nbe a horde of cops here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520875,524295}I know.\NAnyway, you'd better disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524295,527590}But is there really\Na jewelry box in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:53.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528340,533095}I got everything in there out.\NThere shouldn't be anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533095,535931}Something's fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535931,539560}St. Tail wouldn't come to steal\Nsomething that's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540352,542730}Could she have uncovered\Nour scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:07.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542730,547526}And the proof is hidden in this mansion?\NAnd she's coming to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:14.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549320,554909}St. Tail has caused many\Ncriminals to be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555659,559497}Maybe we should clear\Nthe lot off tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:25.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559497,565669}Whatever St. Tail is up to, if there's\Nno place here, there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:30.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566128,570174}If the mansion isn't here,\Nthere's nothing that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:34.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570174,574261}Since it's been decided,\Nlet's tear it down right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575096,576305}Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576430,579183}It's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579183,581018}Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582144,584563}What's all the panic about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585314,588234}Look! Doesn't this\Nbring back memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588234,591695}It's the Miho-chan doll\Nthat you bought for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591695,593447}I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:58.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593447,598536}I bought it for your fifth birthday.\NYou've had it all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:02.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598536,602164}This doll was so very precious\Nto you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:06.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602164,606752}You didn't want any doll\Nother than this Miho-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:11.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606752,611090}Papa, can you make this doll\Nnew again with your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:15.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611799,615803}Well, let's see. I wonder if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:22.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618264,622309}But your precious memories\Nmay disappear too, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624311,626480}Well, I'll keep it the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627565,629024}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:40.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636782,640494}I'm sorry, Ruby.\NI've got to go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:43.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640494,643831}So please entertain our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655634,658804}You're joking!\NI can't let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:04.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659263,664018}Why? We've got to complete\Nthe clearing of the lot by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664018,666061}Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:09.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666061,669148}You said it'd be done tomorrow,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669148,671150}The plans have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:15.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671150,675404}St. Tail's coming!\NThere's no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675404,678741}She can take anything she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:22.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678741,682077}What could be\Nin an empty house anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:25.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682077,685539}A jewelry box. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:29.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685539,689585}Then please let us check if there\Nis really a jewelry box in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691837,693589}There isn't one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693589,697051}Well, if it's not there,\NI'm clearing the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:41.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697509,701513}But should we find one,\Nyou'll have to leave things to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701513,703515}If there are goods\Nworth stealing there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703515,706977}we have an obligation\Nto protect them from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:48.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707728,708812}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708812,710856}But you won't find anything.
Comment: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:51.77,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:711774,711774}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:56.77,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:716779,716779}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721116,724662}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:10.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729625,730668}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732962,734338}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736257,738509}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752815,755317}St. Tail, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:40.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755317,760614}I don't know why, but they're\Nplanning to clear the lot tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760614,762241}You're kidding! But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:50.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763117,770207}I've checked up a bit on that loan company\Nand it seems to be a little shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770916,773419}Meimi, be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:58.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773794,778632}Don't worry. I'll be back\Nwith Michiru's box of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:04.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781051,784638}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786181,787641}{\i1}Please let me get there in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794023,796442}Well? There's nothing here, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:34.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809038,814126}Now, are you satisfied?\NSt. Tail has probably made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:38.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814126,818297}I'll be keeping you to your promise\Nand start clearing the lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818922,821008}I haven't said it's not here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:45.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821592,825596}A promise is a promise.\NI won't stand for this any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825596,828223}The work is going to be started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829475,830893}Even if I stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830893,833604}You should be careful\Nof the chandelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:57.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833604,837191}It'll probably come falling\Nwith the tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842738,844615}What a stubborn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850245,852706}Stop it! Stop it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:14.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853832,854958}What a pesky brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857669,859296}What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859296,862174}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867262,869848}Everyone! Get to your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879441,881777}That's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:45.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881777,885531}Knock her down with the bulldozer!\NNever mind! I'll do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887991,889410}How terrible can he get?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895207,896792}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905217,907428}Darn! Quit scampering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:25.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922317,925362}After her!\NSt. Tail has entered the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931326,933287}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933829,935747}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:51.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947301,951263}It can't be.\NI'm sure it was this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963942,966487}St. Tail, you're in full view.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970115,972159}Give yourself up, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:15.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972159,975454}It's unforgivable to take\Nsomeone's memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985631,988967}I've got you cornered, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988967,990928}You! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996308,999311}Wait a minute!\NWhat are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:43.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999311,1003815}With all this weight,\Nthe chandelier is gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007903,1009238}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021542,1023001}That's where it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024795,1027464}St. Tail, I'll have you\Nshow me your identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:17.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034012,1037224}That idiot! At a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037224,1038392}Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:27.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042312,1047734}If I get rid of this mansion,\Nthere's nothing St. Tail can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052614,1054199}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056368,1058954}I won't let you destroy any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063959,1065127}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066336,1069131}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071091,1073135}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074344,1076054}You pesky worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:16.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091194,1096450}Exactly what I was worried about.\NHe's getting licked! Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:26.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101955,1106168}Goodbye. And I've got\Nthe jewelry box of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107044,1108170}Memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:32.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108587,1112174}What do you mean,\Nmemories, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:36.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112174,1116720}Hey, what are you doing here?\NHold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122976,1125646}And where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125646,1126396}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129524,1130942}Hey, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130942,1132402}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:56.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132402,1136114}I had business with these two.\NNegoro and Momochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136114,1138367}You're under arrest for fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138367,1139368}Fraud?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139368,1142829}These two are convicted criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:08.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142829,1148794}We already know that you two teamed up\Nto swindle this mansion from Mr. Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:10.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148794,1150045}Give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150045,1151088}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162766,1164768}Mother, here, some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165519,1167229}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177948,1179157}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:45.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179157,1185539}Father, my treasure box has come back!\NMy precious memories are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:55.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191128,1195048}I'm glad! Then Michiru's able\Nto return to that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:59.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195549,1199511}Yes. It's only natural because\Nthose two have been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199511,1202013}But the house has\Nbeen damaged so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:06.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202639,1206476}Don't worry.\NThe memories haven't been damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220073,1221742}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:25.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221742,1225203}I've heard that you've made\Na few more memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225203,1229916}Memories! Quit bugging me about them!\NYou act just like someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230792,1232169}Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:37.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232586,1237132}Well, who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:42.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238091,1242095}Oh, forget it!\NIt's none of your concern!
